> **TerraGuard-AI-Agent** is an autonomous environmental intelligence system designed for precision monitoring and risk mitigation — fusing real-time weather telemetry with RAG-powered LLMs to deliver localized, actionable emergency response plans for agricultural and urban sectors. Built for functional safety and low-latency deterministic operation.

