## ✨ Features

```
🛰  Real-time weather telemetry via Open-Meteo (zero cost, no API key)
🧮  MCDA Risk Indexing — deterministic 0–100 threat score
🔍  RAG Knowledge Base — Heatwave, Dust Storm, Flash Flood, Cyclone SOPs
🤖  Gemini 1.5 Flash LLM — localized, grounded emergency action plans
📊  Neural Dashboard — Chart.js 7-day forecast + live metric cards
🔔  Alert Dispatcher — state-transition-triggered, not timer-triggered
📈  SDG 11 & 13 Impact Tracker — resilience index + warning coverage
🔒  Functional Safety — zero hallucination in severity classification
⚡  Low-Latency Sync — configurable deterministic 300s polling cycle
🆓  Fully free stack — Open-Meteo + Gemini Free Tier + no paid services
```

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Language | Python 3.10+ | Core agent logic |
| AI Engine | Google Gemini 1.5 Flash | Plan generation |
| Weather Data | Open-Meteo API | Live telemetry (free, no key) |
| RAG Store | JSON / ChromaDB (optional) | Knowledge base retrieval |
| Scheduling | Python `schedule` + `time` | Deterministic monitoring loop |
| Frontend | HTML5 + Chart.js | Neural dashboard |
| Config | `python-dotenv` | Secure API key management |
| Testing | `pytest` | Unit tests for scorer + retriever |

