## 📁 Project Structure

```
TerraGuard-AI-Agent/
│
├── .gitignore                   ← blocks .env from GitHub
├── .env                         ← YOUR SECRETS (never push this)
├── .env.example                 ← safe template (push this)
├── README.md
├── requirements.txt
│
├── agent/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── monitor.py               ← deterministic polling loop
│   ├── threat_scorer.py         ← MCDA algorithm (0–100)
│   ├── rag_retriever.py         ← RAG pipeline
│   ├── plan_generator.py        ← Gemini API + prompt builder
│   └── alert_dispatcher.py      ← notification dispatch
│
├── knowledge_base/
│   ├── protocols.json           ← RAG documents (SOPs)
│   └── location_config.json     ← geo-coordinates + sector info
│
├── api/
│   ├── weather_client.py        ← Open-Meteo fetch wrapper
│   └── llm_client.py            ← Gemini client (reads from .env)
│
├── ui/
│   ├── dashboard.html           ← Neural Command Interface
│   └── assets/
│       └── chart-config.js
│
├── tests/
│   ├── test_threat_scorer.py
│   └── test_rag_retriever.py
│
└── logs/
    └── .gitkeep                 ← folder tracked, .log files ignored
```

