## 🗺 Supported Locations (Out of the Box)

| Location | Coordinates | Primary Risks |
|---|---|---|
| Abu, Rajasthan | 24.59°N 72.71°E | Heatwave, Dust Storm (Andhi) |
| Jaipur, Rajasthan | 26.91°N 75.78°E | Extreme Heat |
| Mumbai, Maharashtra | 19.07°N 72.87°E | Flash Flood, Cyclone |
| New Delhi, NCT | 28.61°N 77.20°E | Dust Storm + Heat Combo |
| Bengaluru, Karnataka | 12.97°N 77.59°E | Routine / Low Risk |
| Chennai, Tamil Nadu | 13.08°N 80.27°E | Cyclone, Coastal Surge |

Add any location by updating `LOCATION_LAT` and `LOCATION_LON` in your `.env`.

